data.description: 491 Brentwood Drive --- turn-key 3 bed/2 full bath ranch located in Kent. Enclosed front porch which leads you into the main living area. Adjacent to that you'll find the updated bright eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The 3 bedrooms are all located on the main level down the hall with a full bath. Full partially finished basement with a wood burning fireplace and full bathroom + laundry hookups and an extra storage area. 2 car attached garage. All newer windows and newer HWT. Fenced in backyard with a deck and a fire-pit. Kent Local Schools. Neighborhood setting, yet a close proximity to all amenities such as restaurants, shopping, KSU, Route 8 and more! Now is your chance, don't let this opportunity pass you by!
